    <item>
      <title>斯塔默警告重建英国公共财政的预算“痛苦”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/starmer-warns-of-painful-budget-to-rebuild-uk-public-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·史塔默警告称，其政府的十月份预算声明将是“痛苦的”，并要求人们接受“短期痛苦以换取长期利益”，首相利用其上任后的首次重要讲话为可能的增税奠定基础，以重建英国公共财政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/starmer-warns-of-painful-budget-to-rebuild-uk-public-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:40:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登顾问会见中国高级外交官以缓解紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/biden-s-top-security-adviser-lands-in-china-for-official-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的高级国家安全助理杰克·沙利文在北京会见了中国外交部长王毅，目前世界两大经济体正寻求通过对话来管理彼此之间的竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/biden-s-top-security-adviser-lands-in-china-for-official-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 05:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
